        <obo:IAO_0000115>If R &lt;- P o Q is a defining property chain axiom, then (1) R -&gt; P o Q holds and (2) Q is either reflexive or locally reflexive. A corollary of this is that P SubPropertyOf R.</obo:IAO_0000115>
