        <obo:IAO_0000115>Innermost germ layer of the embryo (Campos-Ortega and Hartenstein, 1997). It is formed by the invagination of two anlagen, those of the anterior and posterior midgut (Campos-Ortega and Hartenstein, 1997).</obo:IAO_0000115>
        <oboInOwl:hasDbXref>UBERON:0000925</oboInOwl:hasDbXref>
