        <owl:annotatedTarget>Outer layer of the trunk mesoderm that arises due to mitosis at the end of stage 10 (Campos-Ortega and Hartenstein, 1997). It will give rise to the segmentally-repeated body wall muscles and the fat body (Campos-Ortega and Hartenstein, 1997).</owl:annotatedTarget>
