        <obo:IAO_0000115>The ventrally/medially located ectodermal region of the trunk from which neuroblasts delaminate to form the ventral nerve cord and gnathal ganglia. This region becomes distinct during stage 8 when its cells become enlarged compared to those in the adjacent dorsal ectoderm.</obo:IAO_0000115>
