            </owl:Restriction>
        </rdfs:subClassOf>
        <obo:IAO_0000115>Most posterior of the two main commissures found in each neuromere (absent from A9) of the larval ventral nerve cord and gnathal ganglion (Landgraf et al., 2003; Birkholz et al., 2015; Rickert et al., 2018). In some segments, at some stages these can be further divided into multiple components along the dorsal-ventral axis (Truman et al., 2004; Birkholz et al., 2015; Hartenstein et al., 2018).</obo:IAO_0000115>
        <oboInOwl:hasDbXref>VFB:FBbt_00001120</oboInOwl:hasDbXref>
