            </owl:Restriction>
        </rdfs:subClassOf>
        <obo:IAO_0000115>Neuron that is part of the larval nervous system. Neurons with functional roles in the larva are born during the embryonic phase of neurogenesis and further neurons, with adult-specific roles, are born during the postembryonic phase, which begins during larval development (Lacin and Truman, 2016).</obo:IAO_0000115>
        <oboInOwl:hasDbXref>VFB:FBbt_00001446</oboInOwl:hasDbXref>
        <oboInOwl:hasExactSynonym>embryonic/larval neuron</oboInOwl:hasExactSynonym>
