        <oboInOwl:id>FBbt:00001718</oboInOwl:id>
        <oboInOwl:inSubset rdf:resource="http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/fbbt#cur"/>
        <rdfs:comment>This is the common part of the adult (CA, CC, HG) and larval (CA, CC, PG) ring glands, but terminology seems to be very rarely used for the larva - https://orcid.org/0000-0002-1373-1705.</rdfs:comment>
