            </owl:Restriction>
        </rdfs:subClassOf>
        <obo:IAO_0000115>Neurohemal organ found medially in the anterodorsal part of the larval ring gland, surrounded by cells of the prothoracic gland (Dai and Gilbert, 1991; de Velasco et al., 2004). It is composed of smaller cells than the prothoracic gland (Dai and Gilbert, 1991). It produces juvenile hormone (Dai and Gilbert, 1991; Hartenstein, 1993).</obo:IAO_0000115>
        <oboInOwl:hasAlternativeId>FBbt:00001719</oboInOwl:hasAlternativeId>
        <oboInOwl:hasExactSynonym>larval corpus allatum</oboInOwl:hasExactSynonym>
