            </owl:Restriction>
        </rdfs:subClassOf>
        <obo:IAO_0000115>Imaginal disc that in the adults gives rise to the labrum, anterior and posterior cibarial plates, fish trap bristles, epipharyngeal sclerite and clypeus (Cohen, 1993).</obo:IAO_0000115>
        <oboInOwl:hasDbXref>UBERON:6001765</oboInOwl:hasDbXref>
        <oboInOwl:hasExactSynonym>clypeolabral disc</oboInOwl:hasExactSynonym>
