        <owl:annotatedTarget>Imaginal disc that in the adults gives rise to the labrum, anterior and posterior cibarial plates, fish trap bristles, epipharyngeal sclerite and clypeus (Cohen, 1993).</owl:annotatedTarget>
        <oboInOwl:hasDbXref>FlyBase:FBrf0064789</oboInOwl:hasDbXref>
