        <obo:IAO_0000115>Ring of imaginal tissue located in the embryonic/larval gut, at the junction of the foregut and midgut epithelia in the anterior part of the proventriculus. It is the precursor of the posterior region of the adult foregut.</obo:IAO_0000115>
