            </owl:Restriction>
        </rdfs:subClassOf>
        <obo:IAO_0000115>The entire anatomical structure through which food and its digestion products are ingested, digested and excreted. At its anterior and posterior ends this includes structures that are not foregut or hindgut.</obo:IAO_0000115>
