        <obo:IAO_0000115>Anterior-most region of the adult alimentary canal. It consists (from anterior to posterior) of the posterior the pharynx (cibarium), esophagus, the crop, the stomodeal valve and part of the proventriculus.</obo:IAO_0000115>
