        <obo:IAO_0000115>Set of internal and external structures, originating from abdominal segments 8 and 9, that makes up the genital apparatus (McQueen et al., 2022). It develops from the female genital-primordium part of the genital disc (McQueen et al., 2022).</obo:IAO_0000115>
