        <owl:annotatedProperty rdf:resource="http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115"/>
        <owl:annotatedTarget>Epithelial tube that connects the lateral oviducts to the uterus (Heifetz et al., 2000; Adams and Wolfner, 2007; Kapelnikov et al., 2008; Heifetz et al., 2014; McQueen et al., 2022). It is lined with a chitinous intima, and surrounded by circular muscles (McQueen et al., 2022).</owl:annotatedTarget>
