        <oboInOwl:id>FBbt:00005025</oboInOwl:id>
        <oboInOwl:inSubset rdf:resource="http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/fbbt#cur"/>
        <rdfs:comment>According to Whitten (1980), the most anterior tracheal metamere corresponds to the prothoracic segment.</rdfs:comment>
