        <owl:annotatedProperty rdf:resource="http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115"/>
        <owl:annotatedTarget>Precursor cell of the adult tracheal branches, found in the embryo or larva. Imaginal tracheoblasts originate from the spiracular branches in tracheal metamere 2 to 9, near the junctions with the transverse connectives and from several scattered positions in tracheal metameres 1 and 2.</owl:annotatedTarget>
