            </owl:Restriction>
        </rdfs:subClassOf>
        <obo:IAO_0000115>Terminal branch of the tracheal system. Tracheoles consist of fine cuticular tubes (around 1 micrometre in diameter or less) that extend from individual tracheolar cells. Tracheoles lack a mestracheon.</obo:IAO_0000115>
