        <obo:IAO_0000115>Precursor structure that can be recognized based on its distinct morphology and will give rise to one or more differentiated structures (Tomancak et al., 2002; Hartenstein, 2004). It develops from an anlage and may contain smaller anlage and primordia that will produce substructures (Tomancak et al., 2002).</obo:IAO_0000115>
        <oboInOwl:hasDbXref>UBERON:0001048</oboInOwl:hasDbXref>
        <oboInOwl:hasOBONamespace>fly_anatomy.ontology</oboInOwl:hasOBONamespace>
