                <owl:onProperty rdf:resource="http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000050"/>
                <owl:someValuesFrom rdf:resource="http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FBbt_00111740"/>
            </owl:Restriction>
        </rdfs:subClassOf>
        <obo:IAO_0000115>Neuroblast of the embryonic ventral midline that is a precursor to larval ventral midline neurons, which are found in the ventralmost part of the ventral nerve cord (Kearney et al., 2004). There are four of these cells per neuromere and each divides once to produce two progeny cells (Kearney et al., 2004).</obo:IAO_0000115>
        <oboInOwl:hasDbXref>VFB:FBbt_00005565</oboInOwl:hasDbXref>
        <oboInOwl:hasOBONamespace>fly_anatomy.ontology</oboInOwl:hasOBONamespace>
