            </owl:Restriction>
        </rdfs:subClassOf>
        <obo:IAO_0000115>Malpighian tubule of the embryo. By mid-embryogenesis when cell division ceases, a phase of tubule elongation starts, and the number of cells surrounding the lumen decreases from 6 to 10 to only 2.</obo:IAO_0000115>
        <oboInOwl:hasOBONamespace>fly_anatomy.ontology</oboInOwl:hasOBONamespace>
        <oboInOwl:id>FBbt:00005634</oboInOwl:id>
