        <obo:IAO_0000115>Extended ganglion of the embryonic stomatogastric nervous system. Five to ten neurons are scattered along the axon bundle that extends from the paraesophageal ganglion and that by late embryogenesis grows further posteriorly onto the proventriculus.</obo:IAO_0000115>
