            </owl:Restriction>
        </rdfs:subClassOf>
        <obo:IAO_0000115>Small synaptic neuropil domain of the larval protocerebrum that surrounds the medial lobe of the mushroom body (Pereanu et al., 2010; Hartenstein et al., 2015). It is the larval counterpart of the adult crepine (anterior inferior protocerebrum) (Pereanu et al., 2010).</obo:IAO_0000115>
        <oboInOwl:hasDbXref>VFB:FBbt_00007118</oboInOwl:hasDbXref>
        <oboInOwl:hasDbXref>larvalbrain_neuropil:287</oboInOwl:hasDbXref>
