            </owl:Restriction>
        </rdfs:subClassOf>
        <obo:IAO_0000115>Neuropil region where the larval tritocerebrum intersects with the ventromedial longitudinal domain of the central nervous system (Hartenstein et al., 2018). The anterior widening of the VM fascicle results in an enlargement of the ventromedial domain in the tritocerebrum compared to more posterior neuromeres (Hartenstein et al., 2018).</obo:IAO_0000115>
        <terms:contributor rdf:resource="https://orcid.org/0000-0002-7073-9172"/>
