            </owl:Restriction>
        </rdfs:subClassOf>
        <obo:IAO_0000115>A thin, bilaterally paired synaptic neuropil domain that wraps around the medial lobe of the mushroom body. Many neurons in this domain enter the lobes to form extensive connections with Kenyon cell fibers.</obo:IAO_0000115>
        <oboInOwl:hasDbXref>VFB:FBbt_00045037</oboInOwl:hasDbXref>
        <oboInOwl:hasExactSynonym>CRE</oboInOwl:hasExactSynonym>
        <oboInOwl:hasExactSynonym>IPa</oboInOwl:hasExactSynonym>
