        <owl:annotatedTarget>Intermediate subdivision of the larval anterior commissure (Truman et al., 2004; Birkholz et al., 2015). It is found in all thoracic neuromeres and, at a significantly reduced size, in the labial (S3) and A1 neuromeres (Birkholz et al., 2015). There is one anterior intermediate commissure in the anterior gnathal ganglion (S1/S2) (Kuert et al., 2014).</owl:annotatedTarget>
