        <obo:IAO_0000115>Dorsal subdivision of the larval anterior commissure (Truman et al., 2004; Birkholz et al., 2015). It is thinner than the posterior dorsal commissure (Truman et al., 2004) and is found only in the three thoracic neuromeres (Birkholz et al., 2015).</obo:IAO_0000115>
