        <obo:IAO_0000115>Dorsal subdivision of the larval posterior commissure (Truman et al., 2004; Birkholz et al., 2015). It is thicker than the anterior dorsal commissure (Truman et al., 2004) and is found in the labial (S3) and A1 neuromeres, as well as the three thoracic neuromeres (Birkholz et al., 2015).</obo:IAO_0000115>
