        <obo:IAO_0000115>Any sensory neuron that enters the larval central nervous system via an abdominal nerve. These neurons receive sensory input from internal and external sensory organs of the peripheral nervous system. They may respond to proprioceptive, tactile, nociceptive or other stimuli.</obo:IAO_0000115>
