        <obo:IAO_0000115>Any neuron that develops from neuroblast NB5-2 during the embryonic phase of neurogenesis. The Notch ON hemilineage projects to the dorsal neuropil of both hemispheres and the Notch OFF hemilineage projects to the ventral neuropil of both hemispheres (Mark et al., 2021).</obo:IAO_0000115>
