        <obo:IAO_0000115>Tract of the anterior midline of the larval brain, running from the anterior periesophageal neuropils to the dorso-anterior protocerebrum (Hartenstein et al., 2015). It is formed by fibers from the BAmas1/2 lineages and it grows in length substantially during larval development (Hartenstein et al., 2015).</obo:IAO_0000115>
