        <obo:IAO_0000115>Commissure of the larval gnathal ganglion at late embryonic or larval stages. These are analogous to commissures found in the ventral nerve cord, but there are fewer per neuromere (Kuert et al., 2018; Hartenstein et al., 2018).</obo:IAO_0000115>
        <terms:contributor rdf:resource="https://orcid.org/0000-0002-1373-1705"/>
        <terms:date rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2021-06-15T13:20:15Z</terms:date>
