            </owl:Restriction>
        </rdfs:subClassOf>
        <obo:IAO_0000115>Dorsal portion of the epigynium above the epigynial ventral lobe (McQueen et al., 2022). The two dorsal lobes (left and right) are fused dorsally into a single sclerite (McQueen et al., 2022). It does not harbor sensilla (bristles) (McQueen et al., 2022).</obo:IAO_0000115>
        <terms:contributor rdf:resource="https://orcid.org/0000-0002-1373-1705"/>
        <terms:date rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2022-01-18T11:44:09Z</terms:date>
