        <owl:annotatedTarget>Dorsal portion of the epigynium above the epigynial ventral lobe (McQueen et al., 2022). The two dorsal lobes (left and right) are fused dorsally into a single sclerite (McQueen et al., 2022). It does not harbor sensilla (bristles) (McQueen et al., 2022).</owl:annotatedTarget>
        <oboInOwl:hasDbXref>FlyBase:FBrf0253444</oboInOwl:hasDbXref>
