        <obo:IAO_0000115>A squamous monolayer epithelium that lines the oviduct. Its cells are joined along their lateral membranes by extensive septate junctions, but lack apical zonal adherens junctions (Kapelnikov et al., 2008).</obo:IAO_0000115>
