        </rdfs:subClassOf>
        <obo:IAO_0000115>Any process that modulates the frequency, rate or extent of action potential creation, propagation or termination. This typically occurs via modulation of the activity or expression of voltage-gated ion channels.</obo:IAO_0000115>
