        <oboInOwl:inSubset rdf:resource="http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/pato#scalar_slim"/>
        <rdfs:comment>For any biological use of PATO, the concept that should be used is &apos;mass&apos; and not &apos;weight&apos;. For example, increased weight of an organism.</rdfs:comment>
        <rdfs:label>mass</rdfs:label>
