        <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/PATO_0000141"/>
        <obo:IAO_0000115>A structural quality inhering in a bearer by virtue of whether the bearer forms a bundle of anatomical fibers, as of muscle or nerve.</obo:IAO_0000115>
        <oboInOwl:hasOBONamespace>quality</oboInOwl:hasOBONamespace>
