        <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/PATO_0000141"/>
        <obo:IAO_0000115>A structural quality inhering in the bearer by virtue of the bearer consisting of a single, maximally connected structure.</obo:IAO_0000115>
